= Hear Heartbeat =
'''Sphere:''' Special  
'''Level:''' 4  
'''Range:''' 60 yds  
'''Components:''' V, S, M (cross or holy water)  
'''Duration:''' 1 turn  
'''Casting Time:''' 4 rounds  
'''Area of Effect:''' Varies  
'''Saving Throw:''' None  

== Description ==
Caster hears heartbeat and breathing patterns of subjects within 20-ft, allowing lie detection and sensing invisibility.

== Special Notes ==
* Treated as a [[Prayer]] in this campaign.
* All casting times and durations are increased by an order of magnitude (round → turn, turn → hour, etc).
* Requires cross and/or holy water.
